@startuml
title Siemens U273 Plugin - Parameter Update Sequence

actor "User / DAW Automation" as User
participant "PluginEditor" as Editor
participant "JUCE APVTS" as APVTS
participant "ParameterBridge" as Bridge
participant "Snapshot Backing Store" as Store
participant "PluginProcessor" as Processor
participant "U273DspEngine" as DSP

User -> Editor : move control / automate parameter
Editor -> APVTS : set normalized value
APVTS -> Bridge : parameter changed
Bridge -> Bridge : map normalized -> physical\nvalidate, clamp, precompute
Bridge -> Store : publish complete snapshot\natomic index / safe swap

... later on audio callback ...

Processor -> Bridge : readSnapshot()
Bridge -> Store : load current snapshot
Store --> Bridge : immutable snapshot
Bridge --> Processor : ParameterSnapshot
Processor -> DSP : process(buffer, snapshot)

note right of Bridge
Precompute outside processBlock:
- coefficients
- mode selection
- table references
- validation
end note

@enduml

